		{
			"name": "Admin Analytics",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Get Admin Dashboard",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{accessToken}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/analytics/admin/dashboard",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "analytics", "admin", "dashboard"]
						},
						"description": "Get complete admin dashboard analytics\n\n**Cache TTL**: 10 minutes\n\n**Response**:\n- overview: { totalUsers, totalGroups, totalTasks, activeUsersToday, dauMauRatio }\n- userGrowth: { today, thisWeek, thisMonth, growthRate }\n- revenue: { mrr, arr, thisMonth, lastMonth, growthRate }\n- taskMetrics: { createdToday, completedToday, completionRate, averageTasksPerUser }\n- engagement: { dau, mau, dauMauRatio, retentionRate }\n- topGroups: Array\n- recentUsers: Array"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get User Growth",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{accessToken}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/analytics/admin/user-growth?range=thisMonth",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "analytics", "admin", "user-growth"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "range",
									"value": "thisMonth",
									"description": "thisWeek/thisMonth/thisYear"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Get user growth analytics\n\n**Cache TTL**: 15 minutes\n\n**Query Params**:\n- range: thisWeek/thisMonth/thisYear\n\n**Response**:\n- today, thisWeek, thisMonth\n- growthRate: { daily, weekly, monthly }\n- history: Array of daily growth data"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Revenue Analytics",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{accessToken}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/analytics/admin/revenue",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["v1", "analytics", "admin", "revenue"]
						},
						"description": "Get revenue analytics\n\n**Cache TTL**: 15 minutes\n\n**Response**:\n- mrr: Monthly Recurring Revenue\n- arr: Annual Recurring Revenue\n- thisMonth, lastMonth\n- growthRate\n- bySubscriptionType: { individual, group }\n- history: Array of monthly revenue"
					},
					"response": []
				},
