						"description": "Get user engagement metrics\n\n**Cache TTL**: 15 minutes\n\n**Response**:\n- dau: Daily Active Users\n- mau: Monthly Active Users\n- dauMauRatio: Stickiness ratio\n- averageSessionDuration\n- sessionsPerUser\n- retentionRate: { day1, day7, day30 }"
